\c 15
\s AbaFarisi lababhali basolwa ngenxa yezimiso zabo
\p
\v 1 Kwasekufika kuJesu ababhali labaFarisi ababevela eJerusalema\x + Mark. 7.1-30.\x*, bathi:
\v 2 Kungani abafundi bakho besephula isiko\x + Gal. 1.14. Kol. 2.8.\x* labadala\x + Heb. 11.2.\x*? Ngoba kabagezi izandla zabo, nxa besidla isinkwa.
\v 3 Kodwa waphendula wathi kubo: Lani-ke kungani lisephula umlayo kaNkulunkulu ngenxa yesiko lenu?
\v 4 Ngoba uNkulunkulu walaya, wathi: Hlonipha uyihlo lonyoko\x + Eks. 20.12.Dute. 5.16. Zaga 23.22.\x*; lo\add kuthi\add*: Othuka uyise kumbe unina kumele afe lokufa\x + Eks. 21.17. Levi 20.9. Zaga 20.20.\x*;
\v 5 kodwa lina lithi: Loba ngubani othi kuyise kumbe kunina: \add Ku\add*ngumnikelo\x + 23.18.\x*, loba yini evela kimi ingakusiza,
\v 6 njalo engasoze amhloniphe uyise kumbe unina; ngalokho lenza umlayo kaNkulunkulu\x + Mark. 7.13. Gal. 3.17.\x* ube yize ngenxa yesiko lenu\x + Mark. 7.13. Gal. 3.17.\x*.
\v 7 Bazenzisi, uIsaya waprofetha kuhle ngani, esithi:
\v 8 Lababantu basondela kimi ngomlomo wabo, langendebe bangidumise; kodwa inhliziyo yabo ikhatshana lami\x + Isa.29.13. Hez. 33.31.\x*.
\v 9 Kodwa bangikhonza ngeze, befundisa izimfundiso \add eziy\add*imilayo yabantu\x + Kol. 2.22. Tit. 1.14.\x*.
\v 10 Esebizele kuye ixuku, wathi kilo: Lalelani futhi liqedisise.
\v 11 Kakusikho okungena emlonyeni okungcolisa umuntu; kodwa okuphuma emlonyeni, yikho okungcolisa umuntu\x + Seb. 10.14,15.\x*.
\p
\v 12 Abafundi bakhe basebesondela bathi kuye: Uyazi yini ukuthi abaFarisi bathe ukulizwa lelilizwi bakhubeka?
\v 13 Kodwa waphendula wathi: Sonke isihlahlakazana, uBaba osezulwini angasihlanyelanga, sizasitshunwa\x + Joha. 15.2.\x*.
\v 14 Bayekeleni; bangabakhokheli beziphofu abayiziphofu\x + 23.16,24. Mal. 2.8.\x*; njalo nxa isiphofu sikhokhela isiphofu, zizawela emgodini zombili\x + Luka 6.39.\x*.
\p
\v 15 UPetro wasephendula wathi kuye: Sichasisele lumfanekiso\x + Mark. 7.17.\x*.
\v 16 UJesu wasesithi: Kanti lani lisengabangelakuqedisisa\x + 16.9.\x*?
\v 17 Lilokhe lingaqedisisi yini, ukuthi konke okungena emlonyeni kuya esiswini, futhi kuyelahlelwa ngaphandle\x + 1 Kor. 6.13.\x*?
\v 18 Kodwa izinto eziphuma emlonyeni zivela enhliziyweni\x + Jak. 3.6.\x*; lezi ziyamngcolisa umuntu\x + 15.11,20.\x*.
\v 19 Ngoba enhliziyweni\x + Gen. 6.5.\x* kuvela imicabango emibi, ukubulala, ubufebe, ukuphinga, ukweba, ukufakaza amanga, ukuhlambaza;
\v 20 yizo lezozinto ezimngcolisayo umuntu\x + Jak. 2.4. Hlab. 56.5.\x*; kodwa ukudla ngezandla ezingagezwanga kakumngcolisi umuntu\x + Mark. 7.2,5.\x*.
\s Owesifazana weKhanani
\p
\v 21 UJesu wasesuka lapho, waya kungxenye zeTire lezeSidoni\x + 11.21,22. Mark. 3.8; 7.31. Luka 6.17.\x*.
\v 22 Njalo khangela, owesifazana \add ong\add*umKhanani ovela kuleyomikhawulo, wakhala kuye esithi: Nkosi\x + Hlu. 1.30-33. Mark. 7.26.\x*, Ndodana kaDavida, akungihawukele\x + 9.27.\x*! Indodakazi yami ihlaselwe kubi lidimoni\x + 4.24.\x*.
\v 23 Kodwa kamphendulanga \add nga\add*lizwi. Basebesondela kuye abafundi bakhe bamncenga, bathi: Mxotshe, ngoba uyakhala ngemva kwethu\x + 14.15.\x*.
\v 24 Kodwa waphendula wathi: Kangithunywanga, ngaphandle kuzo izimvu ezilahlekileyo zendlu yakoIsrayeli\x + 10.6. Seb. 3.25,26; 13.46. Roma 15.8.\x*.
\v 25 Kodwa weza wamkhonza wathi: Nkosi, ngisize\x + 8.2.\x*.
\v 26 Kodwa waphendula wathi: Kakukuhle ukuthatha isinkwa sabantwana, loku\add si\add*phosela izinjana.
\v 27 Kodwa yena wathi: Yebo, Nkosi, kodwa lezinjana ziyadla okwemvuthuluka eziwa etafuleni labaninizo\x + 7.6. Fil. 3.2. Isam. 22.15.\x*.
\v 28 UJesu wasephendula wathi kuye: O mama, lukhulu ukholo lwakho! Kakube kuwe njengokuthanda kwakho. Indodakazi yakhe yasisila kusukela kulelohola\x + 9.2.\x*.
\s UJesu usilisa izigulane
\p
\v 29 UJesu wasesuka lapho weza eduzane kolwandle lweGalili\x + Mark. 7.31-37.\x*; wenyukela entabeni wahlala phansi khona.
\v 30 Kwasekusiza kuye amaxuku amakhulu\x + 4.18.\x*, beleziqhuli, iziphofu, izimungulu\x + 11.5.\x*, izingini, labanye abanengi, basebebaphosela enyaweni zikaJesu, wasebasilisa;
\v 31 aze amangala amaxuku\x + 15.31. 18.8. Mark. 9.43.\x*, ebona izimungulu zikhuluma, izingini ziphilile, iziqhuli zihamba, leziphofu zibona\x + 15.31. 18.8. Mark. 9.43.\x*; basebemdumisa\x + 9.8. Luka 2.20; 5.25,26; 7.16; 13.13; 17.15; 18.43; 23.47. Seb. 4.21; 11.18.\x* uNkulunkulu kaIsrayeli\x + Isa. 29.23.\x*.
\s UJesu usuthisa amadoda azinkulungwane ezine
\p
\v 32 UJesu wasebizela kuye abafundi bakhe wathi: Ngilesihelo ngexuku, ngoba sebelami insuku ezintathu, bengelalutho lokudla; njalo kangithandi ukuthi ngibayekele bahambe bengadlanga\x + 14.14-21. Mark. 6.34-44.\x*, hlezi bayathe endleleni.
\v 33 Abafundi bakhe basebesithi kuye: Siza\add zuza\add* ngaphi enkangala izinkwa ezinengi kangaka, ukuthi zisuthise ixuku elikhulu kangaka?
\v 34 UJesu wasesithi kubo: Lilezinkwa ezingaki? Basebesithi: Eziyisikhombisa, lenhlanzana ezinlutshwana\x + 15.36.\x*.
\v 35 Waselaya amaxuku ukuthi ahlale phansi emhlabathini.
\v 36 Wasethatha izinkwa eziyisikhombisa lenhlanzi\x + 15.36.\x*, esebongile wa\add zi\add*hlephula, wa\add zi\add*nika abafundi bakhe, labafundi ixuku.
\v 37 Basebesidla bonke basutha; basebedobha imvuthu ezazisele\x + 26.26, 27. Mark. 8.6; 14.23. Luka 22.17,19. Joha. 6.11,23. Seb. 27.35. Roma 14.6. 1 Kor. 10.30; 11.24. 1 Tim. 4.3,4. Mat. 14.19.\x*, izitsha eziyisikhombisa zigcwele.
\v 38 Lalabo abadlayo babengamadoda azinkulungwane ezine, ngaphandle kwabesifazana labantwana\x + 16.10.\x*.
\v 39 Eseyekele amaxuku ahamba\x + 16.12, Mark. 8.10-21.\x* wangena emkhunjini, weza emikhawulweni yeMagadala\x + Josh. 19.38. Mat. 27.56. Mark. 8.10.\x*.
